      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Creating Risk Alerts on Integration failures\n\n- Add integration_failure in core_risk_sub_types\n\n- Entry in core_risk_alert_config for integration_failure with measurment_config_schema like \n{\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"condition\": {\"type\": \"boolean\"}}, \"required\": [\"threshold\"], \"additionalProperties\": \"false\"}\nwith measurement_operation as Boolean\n\n- Entry in data_risk_alerts_config\n\n- check on integration failure risk alert triggers at two places(common.js & score-refresh.js) before triggering \nINTEGRATION_DATA_FETCH_FAILED kafka event which we are already triggering an event for notification-svc to \nnotify user about the integration failure\n\n- add logic for triggering an alert in common-new.ts\n\n- add logic for generating risk alert message.\n\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Creating Risk Alerts on Integration failures\n\n- Add integration_failure in core_risk_sub_types\n\n- Entry in core_risk_alert_config for integration_failure with measurment_config_schema like \n{\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"condition\": {\"type\": \"boolean\"}}, \"required\": [\"threshold\"], \"additionalProperties\": \"false\"}\nwith measurement_operation as Boolean\n\n- Entry in data_risk_alerts_config\n\n- check on integration failure risk alert triggers at two places(common.js & score-refresh.js) before triggering \nINTEGRATION_DATA_FETCH_FAILED kafka event which we are already triggering an event for notification-svc to \nnotify user about the integration failure\n\n- add logic for triggering an alert in common-new.ts\n\n- add logic for generating risk alert message.\n\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 471
    },
